name: Carrot-Line
description:
Rude Veggies is a collection of 10 radical characters, inspired in the vegetables lovers and my childhood imagination.

Carrot- Line, is the 1st of these radical characters, she is part of the RUDE VEGGIES community, she loves to skate and have fun.

They all are ready to meet new collectors.


Drawing by MNNLLIA
2021
